"""
Snakemake workflow for AOC: preprocessing + recombination + (optional) selection analyses
Multi-gene manifest-driven workflow, updated for Snakemake >= 8.

- Keeps the same preprocessing rules from your AOC Snakefile (get_codons -> macse -> cln -> strike_ambigs -> remove_duplicates -> iqtree -> tn93_cluster -> GARD -> parse_gard -> annotate_lineages)
- Adds the SelectionAnalysis workflow (TN93 distances, FastTree, HyPhy selection suite, tree labelling, RELAX/CFEL, executive summary)
  in a per-gene / per-partition fashion.

Author: Alexander G. Lucaci (original), merged/modernized.
"""

